                    <span class="block mb-4">Where Nature Meets</span>
                    <span class="typewriter gradient-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-secondary">Human Connection</span>
                </h1>
                
                <!-- Animated underline -->
                <div class="relative w-48 h-1 mx-auto mb-10 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white to-transparent"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white animate-text-reveal" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-white/80 text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                    At Casalinga Tours, we believe that the most profound journeys aren't just about where you go, 
                    but how you connect—with nature, with people, and with yourself.
                </p>
                
                <!-- Hero CTA buttons -->
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
                    <a href="#story" 
