                                Casalinga Tours was born in 2010 from a simple yet profound realization: 
                                the most meaningful travel experiences happen when we slow down, connect deeply, 
                                and allow nature to work its restorative magic.
                            </p>
                            
                            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                                Founded by lifelong Mpumalanga residents with a deep love for their homeland, 
                                we started with just one vehicle and a dream—to share the transformative power 
                                of South Africa's natural wonders with travelers seeking more than just a vacation.
                            </p>
                            
                            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                                The name "Casalinga" (Italian for "homely" or "of the home") reflects our philosophy: 
                                every journey should feel like coming home—to yourself, to nature, and to meaningful 
                                human connections.
                            </p>
                            
                            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                                What began as personalized tours for friends and family has grown into a 
                                respected adventure company, but our core values remain unchanged. 
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
